* OSI Model

1. Physical layer (Modem/DSL, Wi-Fi, Hubs)
2. Data link layer (Ethernet, PPP, Switches)
3. Network layer (IP, ICMP)
4. Transport layer (TCP, UDP)
5 and 6. Nobody cares
7. Application layer (HTTP)

